readBAM reads aligned BAM files containing MNase-seq data and formats them into a RData structure suitable for use by NucleR and others

Usage: (runNuclDyn|docker run nucldyn) readBAM --input {bam} --output {RData} --type (single|paired)

Parameters
--input
  Sequence file in BAM format

--output 
  RData structure

--type 
  Type of sequence data: single|paired

